Number = {2},
Pages = {120-121},
Month = {FEB},
Abstract = {Large language models have revolutionized natural language processing.
   The emergence phenomenon is observed in these models and has the
   potential to revolutionize data processing and management. In this
   review, we discuss the concept of emergence in artificial intelligence,
   give detailed examples, and elaborate on the risks and limitations of
   large language models. The review exposes physicians to large language
   models, their advantages, and the inherent opportunities. We also
   describe the limitations and dangers, as these models are expected to
   impact medicine soon.},
