Abstract = {Large Language Models (LLMs) are transforming E-Commerce by powering
   numerous applications such as product recommendation, search,
   classification, question answering, and advertising. Their growing
   adoption in real-world systems highlights their potential, yet
   challenges remain in ensuring accuracy, efficiency, fairness, and
   privacy. This workshop aims to bring together researchers and industry
   practitioners to explore the opportunities and limitations of LLMs in
